{"tid":1879264,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"關於派口罩，我支持剩係派畀手足，歡迎入嚟屌柒我","createTime":"2020-02-14T05:57:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T05:10:17.000Z","uid":38563,"like":140,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"ceccf01988ea05e6bada56c600c876e60f2d2ecb","tid":1879264,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T05:57:07.000Z","msg":"由於而家討論派口罩，所以以下內容只考慮戴唔戴口罩嘅感染機會，其他例如家居傳播/氣溶膠/糞便等等不納入考慮範圍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人話廢中廢老無罩戴又易染病，咪更容易社區爆發，最後傳埋畀手足<br />\n首先無論佢哋戴唔戴罩，佢哋受感染機會都係特別高，原因係生活習慣，衛生常識等等。就算佢哋有一百盒口罩，我相信對降低社區爆發嘅機會大得去邊<br />\n其次啲廢老戴下除下，用完唔洗手，就咁拉低去下巴，亂咁掉，摸完口罩又周圍摸等等，如果個口罩上已經沾咗病毒，根本所有廢老戴同唔戴都係無分別<br />\n當然有罩總比無罩好，但當你資源有限，自然就要好好分配同效益最大化。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而我相信手足們大家都識點戴/除口罩，基本上出街有戴口罩會受飛沫感染嘅機會已經好低，所以派口罩畀手足無疑係最直接最有效防止手足染病嘅方法<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">與其派畀啲潛在傳播者廢老嚟防止佢哋有病時周圍噴<br />\n我寧願派畀手足用嚟防止畀人噴而染病</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再簡單啲嚟講，我用下面兩張圖做對比<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNwGdXu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNwGdXu.jpg&h=978b156f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kaPwBaP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkaPwBaP.jpg&h=2a2daf07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然啦，當社區出現大規模爆發，就算我哋有幾好裝備同注意清潔都好 我哋染病機會都係會大幅上升<br />\n但要知道出現社區爆發嘅主因從來都唔係夠唔夠口罩用<br />\n主因係染病嘅人不斷落嚟之餘仲要有大量無腦藍絲幫手播毒<br />\n畀口罩佢哋根本唔會高效降低社區爆發風險，而既然社區爆發已經出現同加劇，因此我會推薦口罩應該優先派畀手足<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，我無意指責任何人之前點派罩 亦都無意思<br />\n只希望大家將派口罩嘅效益提升，同埋手足少啲機會染病<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">藍絲？死光就好</span>"},{"pid":"49885cc8fe74604764ba48578336a3277f9e2a1d","tid":1879264,"uid":38563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T06:00:45.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b071ad6db4b7878a597a4ee7dff5882ef4cd1642","tid":1879264,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T06:02:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad0e6bfde375c08c71eabcf334d80fb50cfbfdc","tid":1879264,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T06:10:48.000Z","msg":"隔離post嗰千幾個負皮嘅人去咗邊？"},{"pid":"0468b869525d1c0130466cfe73a8d3b5c0df53fb","tid":1879264,"uid":264081,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T06:13:46.000Z","msg":"特別認同第二段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多廢老生活習慣，衛生常識都好差<br />\n戴下除下，用完唔洗手，就咁拉低去下巴，亂咁掉，摸完口罩又周圍摸<br />\n根本係浪費咗個口罩<br />\n<br />\n仲未講有啲廢老明明自己夠但見唔洗錢就拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似台灣咁<br />\n自己人夠用安全先救其他人<br />\n有口罩派都派比手足先<br />\n<br />\n特別想提嘅係 銀髮手足都係手足<br />\n只係唔想浪費珍貴嘅口罩比廢老<br />\n懵盛盛一路拎黃色口罩拎唔到就鬧又唔鬧政府嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b25149a7cd71fe02429874096cd6de69dd5105","tid":1879264,"uid":181703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T06:17:05.000Z","msg":"藍絲死清光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5316ad006473a6fc1f3443c78a2453e712b5cc0","tid":1879264,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T06:24:43.000Z","msg":"我仲等緊人入嚟屌柒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"179ffc08319d874730484d02b62ad757f813b10e","tid":1879264,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T06:41:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17144103ba8d1ca42f7ecfac6583081c0243d8e2","tid":1879264,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T06:56:44.000Z","msg":"政事台無人睇"},{"pid":"6c427ee30299004c60b393ff8f67a1ca19a54539","tid":1879264,"uid":40887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T06:59:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"774a432d7bebe7c236fbc685a1706362001fc830","tid":1879264,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:10:16.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4dab03392b198e584759c707a2d7e2551308d59","tid":1879264,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:35:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab4940c82676849cdd319b83bf5284384b5a6722","tid":1879264,"uid":4105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"774a432d7bebe7c236fbc685a1706362001fc830","tid":1879264,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:10:16.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:44:00.000Z","msg":"正評不解釋"},{"pid":"ab641de33f41f1e8a66120f7d3fc87a62bf7c96b","tid":1879264,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T07:55:07.000Z","msg":"無人夠膽討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"578c59da6adb8870623a89b77348415396f166ed","tid":1879264,"uid":267529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:28:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36510aa7c142d1ff138a1c45bd596667766298e9","tid":1879264,"uid":38563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:30:55.000Z","msg":"p牌都肯幫我象徵性推下post<br />\n其他有獨立思考嘅連登仔呢？"},{"pid":"a29eb56795f04abbdf8f44f736ccb522bf0a83af","tid":1879264,"uid":84668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:42:18.000Z","msg":"藍絲死光就好"},{"pid":"b22565fc673174580930d72f172355524e223052","tid":1879264,"uid":305058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:43:38.000Z","msg":"根本就係<br />\n咁想派嘅話 手足夠口罩先再派俾藍屍囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家手足唔夠仲要同藍屍搶口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3948e80a2a9c695072bcc0c4de12f417185992b7","tid":1879264,"uid":77959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:49:27.000Z","msg":"你唔學另一個po走去屌柒人先，邊個會得閒屌柒你"},{"pid":"6525aff6b2b6fd6dc7a28c2ca8fb743a1d71337f","tid":1879264,"uid":38563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3948e80a2a9c695072bcc0c4de12f417185992b7","tid":1879264,"uid":77959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:49:27.000Z","msg":"你唔學另一個po走去屌柒人先，邊個會得閒屌柒你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:52:05.000Z","msg":"你講得啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以熱門多引戰post都係連登仔一手造成<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58db5178b740d0190ea02e3d527f2cd69f7cbe6","tid":1879264,"uid":170019,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:58:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6db9a86edbaa288a679531854ec02ccf6331df0","tid":1879264,"uid":38563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e58db5178b740d0190ea02e3d527f2cd69f7cbe6","tid":1879264,"uid":170019,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:58:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:03:04.000Z","msg":"其實有冇諗過如果我哋剩係派自己人，先反而有誘因令藍絲投誠<br />\n而且我真係唔見得有幾多藍絲收完口罩可以轉到黃<br />\n<br />\n幫到10個手足重要，定爭取10個藍絲變黃重要？"},{"pid":"308170757251c72b37316f4b53a7119129e99597","tid":1879264,"uid":242323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:21:24.000Z","msg":"認同只派俾手足"},{"pid":"f8eb5e22e7886435d1fb95e4938b634e56108649","tid":1879264,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:22:27.000Z","msg":"入嚟幫你推的"},{"pid":"d0cd13843b5690f19ddc7d92d3e8853cf4056540","tid":1879264,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:22:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80a3a84999a08cd427c0b243e4f23cfe0855e0b2","tid":1879264,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:22:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b62211835b3689b25223a292269ba46269ccaf4","tid":1879264,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:23:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6915d467b3eb2b192681225c1734b5db8fdf57ce","tid":1879264,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8eb5e22e7886435d1fb95e4938b634e56108649","tid":1879264,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:22:27.000Z","msg":"入嚟幫你推的"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:24:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"233c67992fd9fba5ff0b881857661b24f4b67124","tid":1879264,"uid":258230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:24:26.000Z","msg":"太對了"},{"pi